        "type": "practiceLevel1",
        "lessons": [
          {
            "title": "Intro",
            "id": 134830,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Às vezes, queremos formatar parágrafos com quebras de linha.</p><p>Por exemplo, esta música ficaria muito melhor se <code>Raindrops on roses</code> aparecesse em uma linha, <code>Whiskers on kittens</code> na próxima, e assim por diante.</p><webview version=\"2\" visible-if=\"always\" content=\"&lt;h1&gt;My favorite things&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt; Raindrops on roses Whiskers on kittens Bright copper kettles Warm&#xA; woolen mittens &lt;/p&gt;\" /></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Line breaks",
            "id": 134837,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Podemos separar linhas com a ajuda da <strong>tag de quebra de linha</strong>: <code>br</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"html\" name=\"index.html\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"h1\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text value=\"My favorite things\" /><text value=\"&lt;/\" /><text value=\"h1\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"p\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text value=\" Raindrops on roses\" /><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"br\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Whiskers on kittens\" /><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"br\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text value=\" \" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Bright copper kettles \" /><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"br\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text value=\" \" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Warm woolen mittens\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"&lt;/\" /><text value=\"p\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"50\" endIndex=\"54\" /><option startIndex=\"102\" endIndex=\"106\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>&lt;br&gt;</code> seguido de <code>&lt;br&gt;</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Empty tags",
            "id": 134831,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p><code>&lt;br&gt;</code> é uma <strong>tag vazia</strong>. Tags vazias não têm tag de fechamento e nem conteúdo. Elas também são chamadas de tags auto-fechadas.</p><p>Monte a tag de quebra de linha.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"html\" name=\"index.html\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"h1\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text value=\"My favorite things\" /><text value=\"&lt;/\" /><text value=\"h1\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"p\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" Raindrops on roses\" /><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"br\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" Whiskers on kittens\" /><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"br\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" Bright copper kettles\" /><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"br\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" Warm woolen mittens\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"&lt;/\" /><text value=\"p\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"103\" endIndex=\"104\" /><option startIndex=\"104\" endIndex=\"106\" /><option startIndex=\"106\" endIndex=\"107\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"/\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>&lt;</code> seguido de <code>br</code> e finalmente <code>&gt;</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Emphasis",
            "id": 134812,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Existe um elemento para dar ênfase ao texto, ele o torna <em>itálico</em>. É chamado de elemento <code>em</code>. Adicione <code>&lt;em&gt;</code> e <code>&lt;/em&gt;</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"html\" name=\"index.html\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"h1\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text value=\"My favorite things\" /><text value=\"&lt;/\" /><text value=\"h1\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"p\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" Raindrops on \" /><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"em\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text value=\"roses\" /><text value=\"&lt;/\" /><text value=\"em\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"br\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" Whiskers on kittens\" /><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"br\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" Bright copper kettles\" /><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"br\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" Warm woolen mittens\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"&lt;/\" /><text value=\"p\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text type=\"break\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"47\" endIndex=\"51\" /><option startIndex=\"56\" endIndex=\"61\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>&lt;em&gt;</code> seguido de <code>&lt;/em&gt;</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Importance",
            "id": 134813,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Para definir textos como importantes, usamos as tags <code>&lt;strong&gt;</code> e <code>&lt;/strong&gt;</code>. Isso faz com que o texto fique <strong>negrito</strong>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"html\" name=\"index.html\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"h1\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text value=\"My favorite things\" /><text value=\"&lt;/\" /><text value=\"h1\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"p\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" Raindrops on \" /><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"em\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text value=\"roses\" /><text value=\"&lt;/\" /><text value=\"em\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"br\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" Whiskers on \" /><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"strong\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text value=\"kittens\" /><text value=\"&lt;/\" /><text value=\"strong\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"&lt;/\" /><text value=\"p\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"78\" endIndex=\"86\" /><option startIndex=\"93\" endIndex=\"102\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>&lt;strong&gt;</code> seguido de <code>&lt;/strong&gt;</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
